wn or uncertain space =E2=80=93 it=E2=80=99s just too big and expensive, co=
mputationally.  By employing unsupervised =E2=80=9Cguesswork=E2=80=9D strat=
egies, the AI can learn to be =E2=80=9Cluckier=E2=80=9D (said slightly tong=
ue-in-cheek). IOW, it figures out =E2=80=9Cfit=E2=80=9D better than us huma=
ns can define it.



